AttributeList.Text:
How to control and set the UV lamp: To control the lamp the machine needs to be started, all door closed and "LampFaultSignal" checked. After setting the setpoint 0-100 "LampSetpointInput" and enabling "LampEnable", the UV will work.
SafetyLimitSet - can be used to modify output range
E-STOP - always check!
